      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A solid ash staff. It's simple in shape, with much of the natural shape retained along its length, offset only by an iridescent gemstone at its top. The shaft does, however, glow ever-so-slightly, as a result of the electrum runes and thus the enchantments laid into it.",
