      "start": 485797,
      "end": 486195,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"One of the simplest, oldest weapons out there. A favorite of those who operate in the back alleys and tight corridors of southern cities, where a bigger weapon would be too cumbersome. Knives are good for getting in under an opponent's armor, or striking with lightning speed and precision. The blade's balanced and light, making it a capable weapon both in close quarters or as a thrown missile.\"",
