      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A medium-sized bronze sword with a bent, almost axe-like blade. Curved blades are common among the pale elves of the Frost Marches, who enjoy their supposed gracefulness. This weapon is made for chopping through light armor with its crushing blows.",
      "translation": "一把中等大小的青铜剑，剑刃弯曲，几乎呈斧头状。这种弯曲的剑刃在霜冻边境的淡色精灵中十分常见，因为他们认为这种设计更具美感。这种武器之所以被设计出来，就是为了用它那强劲的一击来砍破轻薄的盔甲。",
      "start": 488491,
      "end": 488741,
      "line": 1,
