      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:489134:489604:5640ad05c7b0",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "While oft considered impractical as an arm of war, as its sheer heft precludes the use of a shield and it lacks the reach of a polearm, the straight-edged executioner's blade has nevertheless persisted among adventurers dedicated to Tira who are more than willing to leave themselves open to counterstrikes — after the foe's been flattened by their massive weapon's power.\n        \n        Special Effect: Critical Hits with this weapon inflict Staggered for a turn.",
      "translation": "虽然这种直刃武器常被认为在战争中并不实用——因其重量过大而无法使用盾牌进行防御，且攻击范围也不如长柄武器——但那些热衷于使用这种武器的冒险者们依然坚持使用它。因为在用这种强大武器将敌人击倒之后，他们完全愿意承受敌人的反击。\n\n特殊效果：使用这种武器造成暴击时，会使敌人陷入眩晕状态，持续一回合。",
      "start": 489134,
      "end": 489604,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"While oft considered impractical as an arm of war, as its sheer heft precludes the use of a shield and it lacks the reach of a polearm, the straight-edged executioner's blade has nevertheless persisted among adventurers dedicated to Tira who are more than willing to leave themselves open to counterstrikes — after the foe's been flattened by their massive weapon's power.\\n        \\n        Special Effect: Critical Hits with this weapon inflict Staggered for a turn.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
