      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:490051:490351:feb420bc7ee0",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "The most common weapon for soldiers anywhere in the world, made of a simple wooden haft and a small metal point. The basic spear has good reach and damage, and can punch through some armor, but lacks finesse. The long haft gives the user a great deal of reach, making it easier to keep foes at bay.",
      "translation": "这是世界上各国士兵最常用的武器，由一根简单的木制柄和一个小金属尖端组成。这种基本的长矛具有较远的攻击距离和较强的杀伤力，甚至能够穿透某些类型的盔甲，但缺乏灵活性。由于其较长的柄部，使用者可以拥有更大的攻击范围，从而更轻松地将敌人击退。",
      "start": 490051,
      "end": 490351,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"The most common weapon for soldiers anywhere in the world, made of a simple wooden haft and a small metal point. The basic spear has good reach and damage, and can punch through some armor, but lacks finesse. The long haft gives the user a great deal of reach, making it easier to keep foes at bay.\"",
