      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        This three pronged spear is most commonly seen in the hands of spearfishers after particularly large prey, but in recent years, its grown increasingly popular in the Khor'minoan arena, where retiarii regularly wield one of these alongside a net.\n\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: On hit, causes the target to Bleed for 2 turns.",
      "translation": "这种三叉长矛通常被那些捕获了特别大型猎物的鱼叉手所使用，但近年来，在科尔米诺竞技场中，这种武器也变得越来越受欢迎。在那里，持网战士们经常会同时使用这种长矛和渔网进行战斗。\n\n        <b>特效</b>命中目标后，会使目标在2个回合内持续出血。",
