      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:493567:493912:7f2271f7fb7b",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A spear that formerly belonged to Tiran paladin, and like its master was subjected to all manner of depravity when the Cathedral of the Sunless Deep was ransacked by demons. Now its once-holy aura has been lost, replaced by a hypnotic vibrato when it pierces the air — the spear practically sings in your hand, desperate to be used and abused.",
      "translation": "这柄长矛曾经属于提兰的圣骑士。当无光深渊的大教堂遭到恶魔洗劫时，它与它的主人一样，经历了种种摧残。如今，它那曾经神圣的光环已经消失，取而代之的是一种令人着迷的振动声——当长矛划破空气时，它仿佛在“歌唱”，迫切地渴望被人们使用、被人们挥舞。",
      "start": 493567,
      "end": 493912,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A spear that formerly belonged to Tiran paladin, and like its master was subjected to all manner of depravity when the Cathedral of the Sunless Deep was ransacked by demons. Now its once-holy aura has been lost, replaced by a hypnotic vibrato when it pierces the air — the spear practically sings in your hand, desperate to be used and abused.\"",
