      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "The spear's huge, unwieldy bigger cousin. The pike is bigger than you are tall and deals devastating damage, but its sheer size makes it difficult to wield with precision. As it requires the use of two hands, wielding a pike precludes the use of a shield for defense. Because of this, pikes are generally reserved for use by big blocks of armored footmen on the battlefield.",
      "translation": "长矛的“巨型版本”——这种长矛比你的身高还要长，能够造成毁灭性的伤害，但由于其体积庞大，很难精准操控。由于使用长矛需要双手，因此在战斗中无法同时使用盾牌进行防御。正因如此，长矛通常被用于战场上有重甲保护的步兵部队手中。",
      "start": 494367,
      "end": 494743,
      "line": 1,
