    {
      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:495170:495518:bcad3a5fc5b1",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "What's better than an axe? An axe on a big, long haft that lets you hit people further away from you! Poleaxes are heavier and less agile than a normal battleaxe or spears, but they pack immense punch and can chop through armor. These weapons are favored by orcish raiders, whose second ranks can swing these immense axes over their shield walls.",
      "translation": "有什么比斧头更厉害的呢？当然是那种柄长且沉重的斧头了——这样的斧头能让使用者从更远的距离攻击敌人！长柄斧虽然比普通的战斧或长矛更重，灵活性也较差，但它们具备惊人的破坏力，甚至能够砍穿盔甲。这种武器深受兽人掠夺者的喜爱，他们的二线战士就能在盾墙后挥舞这些沉重的斧头进行攻击。",
      "start": 495170,
      "end": 495518,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"What's better than an axe? An axe on a big, long haft that lets you hit people further away from you! Poleaxes are heavier and less agile than a normal battleaxe or spears, but they pack immense punch and can chop through armor. These weapons are favored by orcish raiders, whose second ranks can swing these immense axes over their shield walls.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
