      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:495971:496221:d9d051b77b23",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A simple design, with a heavy cutting head on a smooth haft. Useful for both the woodlands survivor and the warrior, a one-handed axe deals out punishing blows more often than similar weapons, though it's not particularly good against armored foes.",
      "translation": "这种斧头设计简单，刀头沉重，刀柄光滑。无论是森林生存者还是战士，这种单手斧都能带来强有力的打击——与同类武器相比，它更常能造成有效的伤害，不过在对抗装甲敌人时效果并不显著。",
      "start": 495971,
      "end": 496221,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A simple design, with a heavy cutting head on a smooth haft. Useful for both the woodlands survivor and the warrior, a one-handed axe deals out punishing blows more often than similar weapons, though it's not particularly good against armored foes.\"",
