      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:496631:497079:ebc34a9d03a1",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A mage-forged pickaxe, made from glittering meteorite iron. She's got a hell of a lot of heft to her, and the axehead's beautifully curved, too perfect for modern smithing to replicate without some exceptional magical assistance. It's decorated with a number of small fetishes and charms, arranged in carefully-cultivated patterns by an obsessive owner.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Gains +100 Attack Power when attacking Constructs.",
      "translation": "这把由法师锻造的镐，是用闪闪发光的陨铁制成的。它的重量相当可观，镐头也呈优美的弧线形状——这样的工艺，如果没有强大的魔法辅助，现代铁匠根本无法复制。镐头上还装饰着许多小符咒和护身符，它们都是由这位充满执念的主人精心排列而成的。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>攻击构造物时，攻击力增加100。",
      "start": 496631,
      "end": 497079,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A mage-forged pickaxe, made from glittering meteorite iron. She's got a hell of a lot of heft to her, and the axehead's beautifully curved, too perfect for modern smithing to replicate without some exceptional magical assistance. It's decorated with a number of small fetishes and charms, arranged in carefully-cultivated patterns by an obsessive owner.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Gains +100 Attack Power when attacking Constructs.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
      "translationModel": "huihui_ai/hy-mt1.5-abliterated:latest",
      "translatedAt": "2026-06-27T22:01:38.614Z"
