      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:497607:497991:cdc99f7b2900",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        It is said a long-forgotten god possesses this axe, driving its wielder on to commit ever bloodier acts. Anyone with a lick of sense knows, of course, that such a thing is impossible...\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Chaos reigns, 33% chance on any action to inflict Hysteria on the wielder for 4 turns, increasing damage dealt by +40% and damage taken by +20%.",
      "translation": "据说，有一位被人们长久遗忘的神明拥有这把斧头，它驱使使用者不断犯下更加残忍的罪行。当然，任何稍有理智的人都会明白，这种事情根本是不可能发生的……\n        \n        <b>特效</b>混乱肆虐，任何行动都有33%的概率使使用者陷入4回合的“歇斯底里”状态，在此状态下，造成的伤害会增加40%，而受到的伤害则会增加20%。",
      "start": 497607,
      "end": 497991,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        It is said a long-forgotten god possesses this axe, driving its wielder on to commit ever bloodier acts. Anyone with a lick of sense knows, of course, that such a thing is impossible...\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Chaos reigns, 33% chance on any action to inflict Hysteria on the wielder for 4 turns, increasing damage dealt by +40% and damage taken by +20%.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
      "translationModel": "huihui_ai/hy-mt1.5-abliterated:latest",
