      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:499888:500177:95c47583b9d3",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "One of the simplest weapons ever devised: a big stick. About six feet long and made of smooth, polished heartwood, the quarterstaff makes a fine walking stick and hits startlingly hard when used as a club. As this staff lacks a focusing crystal, it's not terribly valuable to a magician.",
      "translation": "有史以来最简单的武器之一，就是一根大棍子。这种棍子长约六英尺，由光滑、经过打磨的木质部分制成，既可以用作方便的拐杖，用作棍棒时也能产生惊人的打击力。由于这种棍子没有聚焦水晶，因此对魔法师来说并没有太大的价值。",
      "start": 499888,
      "end": 500177,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"One of the simplest weapons ever devised: a big stick. About six feet long and made of smooth, polished heartwood, the quarterstaff makes a fine walking stick and hits startlingly hard when used as a club. As this staff lacks a focusing crystal, it's not terribly valuable to a magician.\"",
