      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:500600:500990:91b4d338e162",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A heavy staff set on one end with a magically-treated focusing stone, and on the other with a short bronze sword-blade, the same as one might find on the belt of a Khor'minoan soldier. These weapons keep your enemies at bay should they manage to close through a withering hail of magical attacks empowered by it — but don't expect it to hit with the same authority as a dedicated polearm.",
      "translation": "一端装有经过魔法处理的聚焦石，另一端则配有一把短青铜剑刃的沉重棍棒，这种武器与科尔米诺士兵腰带上的武器颇为相似。一旦敌人试图突破这连续不断的魔法攻击范围，这些武器就能将他们击退——但请注意，它们的攻击力远不如专门的长柄武器。",
      "start": 500600,
