      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A massive greathammer with a solid bronze head, far too heavy for most warriors to swing around with the uncaring furor that the Kervus warriors do. These hammers get their name from their primary use, boarding enemy vessels from an orcish longship and bringing down their masts so that there is no hope of escape.\"",
