      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        One of Vitruvius' masterworks, this hammer's dual heads are perpetually covered in a thin layer of ice not unlike one often sees on grass after a cold Frost Marches night. Upon particularly brutal impacts, the brittleness of ice is conveyed to the target's armor as part of the hammer's enchantment.\n\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: On critical hits, this weapon applies the Sundered status effect.",
      "translation": "作为维特鲁威的杰作之一，这种锤子的双头表面始终覆盖着一层薄冰，这种冰层与寒冷的霜冻之夜后草地上常见的冰层极为相似。在那些特别猛烈的撞击中，冰的脆弱性会通过这种锤子的魔法效果传递到目标的盔甲上。\n\n        <b>特效</b>在暴击时，这种武器会施加“分裂”状态效果。",
      "start": 513308,
      "end": 513719,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        One of Vitruvius' masterworks, this hammer's dual heads are perpetually covered in a thin layer of ice not unlike one often sees on grass after a cold Frost Marches night. Upon particularly brutal impacts, the brittleness of ice is conveyed to the target's armor as part of the hammer's enchantment.\\n\\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: On critical hits, this weapon applies the Sundered status effect.\"",
