      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:527686:528021:4a4ef1e7dd1c",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A copper wand set with a heavy red gem and engraved with occultic runes representing elemental Fire. Even the most novice of mages can channel a gout of flame through this arcane implement, making it a steadfast backup for those sorcerers who'd prefer to memorize defensive spells or weapon-empowering ones instead of simple strikes.",
      "translation": "一根铜制法杖，上面镶嵌着一颗沉重的红色宝石，同时还刻有象征火元素的神秘符文。即便是最初级的法师，也能通过这根法杖释放出火焰攻击。对于那些更倾向于记忆防御性法术或增强武器的法术，而非简单的攻击法术的法师来说，这无疑是一件非常实用的辅助工具。",
      "start": 527686,
