      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:529028:529571:e30967c7e7ed",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "property_text",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "This mystic bow has thin pieces of copper attached along its length in such a way as to create a spiral around the riser. Electrum runes are inscribed into each one and gently pulsate with supernatural light. While these passively imbue any arrow loosed from the bow with power drawn from a storm, this is only a side benefit for many of its wielders. For — through the runes and the layout of the copper — mages are able to better focus their spells through their arrows, making this style of bow popular with any prospective mystic archer.",
      "translation": "这种神秘的弓在弓身上镶嵌着细薄的铜片，这些铜片以螺旋状排列在弓身上。每片铜片上都刻有电银符文，这些符文会散发出超自然的光芒。当箭从这种弓中射出时，这些铜片会被动地为箭赋予源自风暴的力量，但对于许多使用这种弓的人来说，这仅仅是一个附加效果而已。 通过那些符文以及铜制弓身的构造设计，法师们能够更精准地引导他们的法术通过箭矢释放，因此这种风格的弓箭深受所有有志于成为神秘弓箭手的者的青睐。",
      "start": 529028,
      "end": 529571,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"This mystic bow has thin pieces of copper attached along its length in such a way as to create a spiral around the riser. Electrum runes are inscribed into each one and gently pulsate with supernatural light. While these passively imbue any arrow loosed from the bow with power drawn from a storm, this is only a side benefit for many of its wielders. For — through the runes and the layout of the copper — mages are able to better focus their spells through their arrows, making this style of bow popular with any prospective mystic archer.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "other",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_property_text",
