      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        Such was the retiarius' skill with her trident, she had no need for the net.\n\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Single-target, non-weapon, non-spell powers that deal damage inflict Staggered for 2 turns, and have an additional 30% chance of inflicting Prone for 1 turn.",
      "translation": "这位持三叉戟的战士运用这种武器的技巧如此娴熟，以至于她根本不需要使用网来辅助战斗。\n\n        <b>特效</b>这些单体攻击型、非武器类、非法术类的技能在造成伤害的同时，会令目标在2个回合内处于摇晃状态，并且有30%的概率使目标在1个回合内陷入虚弱状态。",
