      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:537472:537707:5203e65b1807",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A heavy war pick, complete with a counterweight and nasty point. Heavy and unwieldy, it nevertheless is quite lethal against heavily armored opponents, negating the benefits of their protection while leaving all the drawbacks intact.",
      "translation": "这是一种重量沉重的战锤，配有配重装置，其末端也极其锋利。虽然体积庞大且使用起来不够灵活，但面对装甲厚重的敌人时，它却能发挥出极其致命的效果——完全抵消了那些厚重装甲带来的防护优势，同时保留着所有其他缺点。",
