      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:538796:539205:8282a6ab779a",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "One of Vitruvius' masterworks, even the hilt of this sword is warm to the touch. Imbued with elemental fire by runes inscribed upon the length of the undulating blade, a single hit from this blade is enough to leave foes scorched in its wake. The raw power does also make casting magic through the blade easier, making this a valuable tool for the more martially-inclined mage or magically-inclined warrior.",
      "translation": "作为维特鲁威的杰作之一，就连这把剑的剑柄触感也都十分温暖。剑身镌刻着符文，这些符文蕴含着元素之火，因此，只要用这把剑砍出一击，就能让敌人身上留下灼热的痕迹。这种强大的力量还使得通过剑刃施展魔法变得更加容易，因此，对于那些更倾向于运用武力或魔法的法师与战士来说，这无疑是一把极其珍贵的武器。",
      "start": 538796,
      "end": 539205,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"One of Vitruvius' masterworks, even the hilt of this sword is warm to the touch. Imbued with elemental fire by runes inscribed upon the length of the undulating blade, a single hit from this blade is enough to leave foes scorched in its wake. The raw power does also make casting magic through the blade easier, making this a valuable tool for the more martially-inclined mage or magically-inclined warrior.\"",
