      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:540276:540875:94563965c6f8",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A hand sickle — while the simple wood handle and iron blade are unassuming, the point and edge expose its intention for reaping lives, rather than crops. A favorite of the occasional tengu-led nekomata rebellion against kitsune and tanuki dominion in the Old Country's past due to its concealable nature and plausible deniability as a farming implement, the sickle is made to pierce padded cloth and leather with its wicked point. Along with the garden trowel, these later became popularised in stories about those historical periods, especially about a clan of weasel assassins who wielded these.",
      "translation": "一把手镰刀——虽然它那简单的木柄和铁刃看起来并不显眼，但其锋利的刀尖无疑昭示了它的用途：收割生命，而非庄稼。在古代，这种镰刀常常被那些受天狗领导的猫妖用来反抗狐与狸的统治。由于它外形普通，完全可以被当作农具使用，因此人们很难怀疑它的真正用途。而它那锋利的刀尖，更是能够轻易穿透厚布与皮革。 与园艺铲一起，这些工具后来在描绘那些历史时期的故事中广为流传，尤其是那些使用这些工具的鼬鼠刺客家族的故事。",
      "start": 540276,
      "end": 540875,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A hand sickle — while the simple wood handle and iron blade are unassuming, the point and edge expose its intention for reaping lives, rather than crops. A favorite of the occasional tengu-led nekomata rebellion against kitsune and tanuki dominion in the Old Country's past due to its concealable nature and plausible deniability as a farming implement, the sickle is made to pierce padded cloth and leather with its wicked point. Along with the garden trowel, these later became popularised in stories about those historical periods, especially about a clan of weasel assassins who wielded these.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
      "translationModel": "huihui_ai/hy-mt1.5-abliterated:latest",
      "translatedAt": "2026-06-27T22:02:40.460Z"
    },
