      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:541314:541947:49c5a98bb084",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A short, simple blade made for rapid strikes in close-quarters combat. Its length is slightly curved, the edge meticulously sharp, and the whole thing comes with a scabbard of lightweight lacquered wood. A small sidearm to a longer, heavier weapon, perhaps, or for situations where a heavier weapon would be impractical.\n\n        Although the fact that the weapon's made of iron is somewhat worrisome, the grip is secure and it feels fast and balanced enough. This isn't a weapon for overcoming armor, but circumventing it instead.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical strikes with this weapon deal 15% more damage.",
      "translation": "这是一种短小精悍的刀刃，专为近战中的快速攻击而设计。它的刀身略带弯曲，刀刃经过精心打磨，变得极其锋利，整个刀具配有一个由轻质漆木制成的刀鞘。这种小型武器或许可以作为更长、更沉重的武器的补充，或者在那些使用重型武器会显得不切实际的情况下使用。\n\n        虽然这种武器是由铁制成的，这一事实确实令人有些担忧，但它的握把设计非常牢固，使用起来感觉速度足够快，而且平衡性也很好。这种武器并不是用来突破护甲的，而是用来绕过护甲的。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>使用这种武器进行暴击时，造成的伤害会增加15%。",
      "start": 541314,
      "end": 541947,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A short, simple blade made for rapid strikes in close-quarters combat. Its length is slightly curved, the edge meticulously sharp, and the whole thing comes with a scabbard of lightweight lacquered wood. A small sidearm to a longer, heavier weapon, perhaps, or for situations where a heavier weapon would be impractical.\\n\\n        Although the fact that the weapon's made of iron is somewhat worrisome, the grip is secure and it feels fast and balanced enough. This isn't a weapon for overcoming armor, but circumventing it instead.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical strikes with this weapon deal 15% more damage.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
      "translationModel": "huihui_ai/hy-mt1.5-abliterated:latest",
      "translatedAt": "2026-06-27T22:02:43.506Z"
    },
