      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "One of a pair of magical swords. Forged by a Jassiran metalsmith and enchanted, they're formidable weapons. As Maidensbane would put it, better wielded than not.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Hitting a demon casts Song of Storms on you.\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: 33% chance to cast Obliterate Demon on any hit while you have Song of Storms active.",
