      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:544383:545068:25fdfbee6f12",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "One of a pair of magical swords. Forged by a Jassiran metalsmith and enchanted, they're formidable weapons. As Maidensbane would put it, better wielded than not.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Gain Moon's Mercy for 6 turns on hitting someone in the last 40% of their hitpoints. While you have Moon's Mercy, gain a shield equal to the frost damage you do.\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: When you have both Moon's Mercy and Star's Illumination, hitting a non-boss enemy in the last 20% of their hp instantly downs them.\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: When you have both Sun's Might and Moon's Mercy, deal +50% damage to enemies in the first 30% of their hp and last 20% of their hp.",
      "translation": "这是一对魔法剑中的一把。由贾西兰的铁匠锻造并施加了魔法，它们是极其强大的武器。用梅登斯贝恩的话来说，掌握使用这些剑总比不使用要好得多。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>在攻击生命值只剩下40%的敌人时，可以获得“月之恩典”，使自己在接下来的6个回合内受到伤害减免。在拥有“月之恩典”期间，你还会获得一个与自己造成的冰冻伤害相当的护盾。\n        <b>额外奖励</b>当你同时拥有“月之慈悲”和“星之照耀”这两种能力时，攻击那些生命值只剩下20%以下的非首领敌人，就能立即将其击败。\n        <b>额外奖励</b>当你同时拥有“太阳之力”与“月之慈悲”时，对敌人生命值前30%和后20%的部分，造成的伤害将会增加50%。",
      "start": 544383,
      "end": 545068,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"One of a pair of magical swords. Forged by a Jassiran metalsmith and enchanted, they're formidable weapons. As Maidensbane would put it, better wielded than not.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Gain Moon's Mercy for 6 turns on hitting someone in the last 40% of their hitpoints. While you have Moon's Mercy, gain a shield equal to the frost damage you do.\\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: When you have both Moon's Mercy and Star's Illumination, hitting a non-boss enemy in the last 20% of their hp instantly downs them.\\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: When you have both Sun's Might and Moon's Mercy, deal +50% damage to enemies in the first 30% of their hp and last 20% of their hp.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
