      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "One of a pair of magical swords. Forged by a Jassiran metalsmith and enchanted, they're formidable weapons. As Maidensbane would put it, better wielded than not.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Hitting a debuffed enemy proliferates debuffs to all other enemies.\n        <b>Set Bonus</b>: Bonus damage against enemies with at least 3 debuffs.",
      "translation": "这是一对魔法剑中的一把。由贾西兰的铁匠锻造并施加了魔法，它们是极其强大的武器。用梅登斯贝恩的话来说，拥有这样的武器总比没有要好。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>攻击处于虚弱状态的敌人会使该虚弱状态扩散到所有其他敌人身上。\n        <b>额外奖励</b>：对至少带有3个减益状态的敌人造成额外伤害。",
      "start": 550482,
      "end": 550836,
      "line": 1,
