      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:551843:552465:59f203432ea4",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A small dagger-like weapon shaped suspiciously like a garden trowel — you swear you've seen some of the kitsune working in their vegetable gardens with these, although they can't possibly be using actual weapons to do their digging, right?\n        \n        Like most other kitsune weapons, this one's made of iron instead of bronze, although it's clear that the weapon's soft and meant to be resharpened between uses. This is more a tool that happens to have killing power, as opposed to a weapon which is serviceable as a tool.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: On hit, causes the target to Bleed for 2 turns.",
      "translation": "一种外形酷似园艺铲的小型匕首状武器——你肯定会觉得，那些狐狸精在打理菜园时肯定用过这种东西，不过它们总不可能真的用真正的武器来挖土吧？\n        \n        与大多数其他九尾狐武器不同，这件武器是由铁而非青铜制成的。不过，从外观上可以看出，这种武器相当柔软，使用之后需要重新磨利才能继续使用。实际上，它更像是一种具有杀伤力的工具，而非一种同时具备武器与工具双重功能的武器。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>命中目标后，会使目标在2个回合内持续出血。",
      "start": 551843,
      "end": 552465,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A small dagger-like weapon shaped suspiciously like a garden trowel — you swear you've seen some of the kitsune working in their vegetable gardens with these, although they can't possibly be using actual weapons to do their digging, right?\\n        \\n        Like most other kitsune weapons, this one's made of iron instead of bronze, although it's clear that the weapon's soft and meant to be resharpened between uses. This is more a tool that happens to have killing power, as opposed to a weapon which is serviceable as a tool.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: On hit, causes the target to Bleed for 2 turns.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
      "translationStatus": "ollama_translated",
      "translationModel": "huihui_ai/hy-mt1.5-abliterated:latest",
      "translatedAt": "2026-06-27T22:03:08.316Z"
