      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:565422:565883:160e21696120",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A greataxe forged deep in the mountains of Zhenna, a land steeped in dark primordial magics. Though perhaps it was once mundane, a common woodsman's axe, the bronze blade is now encrusted with the sap of an ancient wyld tree hewn down by human hands. Velun unleashed a terrible wrath upon the greedy men that sought the lifeblood of a fey for their own profits, but even the Green Lord's magic could not fully wipe away the sin stained on this weapon's blade.",
      "translation": "这把巨斧是在赞纳山脉深处锻造的，那里充满了黑暗的原始魔法。虽然它原本可能只是一把普通的伐木斧，但如今，它的青铜刀刃上已经覆盖着人类砍伐下来的古老野树的树液。维伦向那些为了一己私利而试图夺取精灵生命之力的贪婪之徒发起了猛烈的报复，然而，就连绿之主的魔法也无法彻底抹去这把武器刀刃上留下的罪孽痕迹。",
      "start": 565422,
      "end": 565883,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A greataxe forged deep in the mountains of Zhenna, a land steeped in dark primordial magics. Though perhaps it was once mundane, a common woodsman's axe, the bronze blade is now encrusted with the sap of an ancient wyld tree hewn down by human hands. Velun unleashed a terrible wrath upon the greedy men that sought the lifeblood of a fey for their own profits, but even the Green Lord's magic could not fully wipe away the sin stained on this weapon's blade.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
