      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        The half-bow — a shortbow suited for someone of your small stature. Not as impressive as [silly|Azami's|Ishida-San's] azusa-yumi, but still it has been yours ever since you were a kit. While your mother favored the naginata and you learned the forms of that weapon anyway, you've always felt more at home with string and fletching. Archery, after all, is still a respectable calling for a kitsune.\n\n        ...Now today, you put your life in the hands of your weapon and your training.",
      "translation": "半弓——这种短弓非常适合你这样的身材。不过，它的威慑力显然没有…… [silly|Azami的|石田先生的] 梓由美，但从你还是只只小狐狸的时候起，这些武器就已经属于你了。虽然你的母亲更喜欢长刀，而你也确实学习了那种武器的使用方法，但你对弓箭始终有着更深厚的感情。毕竟，对于一只狐狸来说，射箭仍然是一份值得尊敬的职业。\n\n……而今天，你将自己的生命交到了这些武器和自己的训练成果手中。",
      "start": 567168,
      "end": 567667,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        The half-bow — a shortbow suited for someone of your small stature. Not as impressive as [silly|Azami's|Ishida-San's] azusa-yumi, but still it has been yours ever since you were a kit. While your mother favored the naginata and you learned the forms of that weapon anyway, you've always felt more at home with string and fletching. Archery, after all, is still a respectable calling for a kitsune.\\n\\n        ...Now today, you put your life in the hands of your weapon and your training.\"",
