      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:568078:568423:f1ec4d504b9a",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "By kitsune custom and tradition, the glaive is the quintessential woman's weapon, and doubly so for someone with your lineage. Ever since you were a girl, your mother painstakingly trained you in the use of the naginata, mornings upon mornings going through the forms... \n\n        ... And today, that training holds your life in the balance.",
      "translation": "根据狐族的习俗与传统，长刀是女性最理想的武器，而对于像你这样拥有高贵血统的人来说，这种武器更是不可或缺。从你还是个小女孩的时候起，你的母亲就孜孜不倦地教你如何使用长刀，一天又一天地重复那些训练动作……\n\n……而今天，正是这些训练在关键时刻挽救了你的生命。",
      "start": 568078,
      "end": 568423,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"By kitsune custom and tradition, the glaive is the quintessential woman's weapon, and doubly so for someone with your lineage. Ever since you were a girl, your mother painstakingly trained you in the use of the naginata, mornings upon mornings going through the forms... \\n\\n        ... And today, that training holds your life in the balance.\"",
