      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:569527:569955:04804f9c589c",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        A light-colored wood staff about five feet long, multiple mushroom caps bloom out across its bottom and tip. Each mushroom blends into a beautiful array of colors cast over a thick moss, stretching up its length until meeting a wide-brimmed cap. Tucked just beneath the cap out of sight is a magical focus, perfect for magic users.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Allows the use of <i>Summon Sporeling</i>.",
      "translation": "一根长约五英尺的浅色木杖，其底部和顶端都长出了多个蘑菇状的结构。每个“蘑菇”都呈现出绚丽的色彩，这些色彩覆盖在厚厚的苔藓之上，一直延伸到木杖的顶端，那里还有一个宽边帽状的结构。而在这个帽状结构下方，隐藏着一个神奇的聚焦点，非常适合魔法师使用。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>：允许使用 <i>召唤孢子幼体</i>.",
      "start": 569527,
      "end": 569955,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        A light-colored wood staff about five feet long, multiple mushroom caps bloom out across its bottom and tip. Each mushroom blends into a beautiful array of colors cast over a thick moss, stretching up its length until meeting a wide-brimmed cap. Tucked just beneath the cap out of sight is a magical focus, perfect for magic users.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Allows the use of <i>Summon Sporeling</i>.\"",
