      "id": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js:570586:571082:89f4039b20c7",
      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        A four-pronged throwing star, intricately etched and designed to look like a flower while being every bit as deadly as it is beautiful. While it would have only been good for harassing enemies were it completely mundane, the gleam upon its edges and the way it returns to the thrower after being set into motion implies that it's more than the gaudy bauble it purports to be.\n\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical hits made while wielding this weapon gain +50 Crit Effectiveness.",
      "translation": "这种四翼飞镖雕刻精美，其造型看似花朵，却兼具极高的杀伤力与美观性。如果它的边缘没有那种闪烁的光芒，如果它在飞出后不会自动回到投掷者手中，那么它或许只是一种用来骚扰敌人的普通道具罢了。但正是这些独特的设计特点，让它超越了普通装饰品的范畴，展现出别具一格的魅力。\n\n        <b>特效</b>使用这种武器进行暴击时，暴击效果的有效性会增加50%。",
      "start": 570586,
      "end": 571082,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        A four-pronged throwing star, intricately etched and designed to look like a flower while being every bit as deadly as it is beautiful. While it would have only been good for harassing enemies were it completely mundane, the gleam upon its edges and the way it returns to the thrower after being set into motion implies that it's more than the gaudy bauble it purports to be.\\n\\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical hits made while wielding this weapon gain +50 Crit Effectiveness.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
