      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "possible_text",
      "shouldTranslate": false,
      "original": "A sharp jolt of searing pain races through your arm as a palpable aura of malice emanates from the fallen Dawnsword. Looks like you're becoming a bit too much of a goody-two-shoes for the weapon's sensibilities. It doesn't quite have the power to stop you from lugging it around, but it can certainly prevent you from wielding it in the service of causes it doesn't like.",
      "translation": "",
      "start": 575074,
