      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": false,
      "original": "\n        The pride and joy of the Order of the Oriflamme, granted to that cadre of elite Lumian paladins by the goddess herself. Casual inspection suggests that it's little more than an elaborate sword hilt with far too much gilding, but upon activation by the wielder a blade of blazing brilliance bursts forth from the guard, capable of cleaving through metal with ease. Two decades underground hasn't tarnished it any, and it still gleams as if it were brand new. [pc.swornGod lumia\n            |There's no weapon better suited for a valkyrie like you, the cream of the crop when it comes to the goddess of light's holy warriors.\n            |That it actually works for you says something in and of itself; although whether you personally like the implications is another matter... \n        ]\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: When wielded, this weapon grants the Deflection ability.",
