      "original": "\n        A brace of throwing daggers that seem to have a mind of their own. Each blade is shot through with silver and gold veins that make the whole ensemble resemble a beautifully feathered wing. You can feel wind and sun alike dancing in your hands when you hold them, and each one returns to the brace after being thrown. \n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Grants immunity to the Disarmed effect.\n        ",
