      "original": "A two-handed, double-headed greataxe pulled from an armory with little in the way of distinctions, but when wielded by anyone wearing the Adjudicator clothing, the weapon becomes electrified, imbued with the power of storms. Agnimitra can create guitar strings made of pure lightning along the axe’s handle to play... well, something akin to music.",
