      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        A titanic smithing hammer made of stone and mystical crystal, once wielded by the forge golem of Dracia. This hammer was used to craft blades of legend and armor made of dragonscale, but lay forgotten in Cloudreach Tower for centuries after the island's fall. It still carries the heat of the forge within its enchanted facets, waiting to be unleashed on the anvil or on your foes.",
      "translation": "这把由石头与神秘水晶制成的巨型锻造锤，曾由德拉西亚的锻造魔像使用。这把锤子曾被用来打造传说中的刀刃以及由龙鳞制成的铠甲，但在岛屿陷落之后，它被遗弃在云达塔中，沉睡了几个世纪。如今，它的每一面都还蕴含着锻造时的高温，等待着在铁砧上发挥作用，或是用来击败你的敌人。",
      "start": 586804,
