      "original": "\n        A Minoan legionnaire's gladius. This one has been hoisted in victory time and time again, its hilt worn and weathered... but never broken.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: While wielding this weapon, your attacks ignore 20% of the target's Armor.",
