      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "\n        A light and wieldy shortbow of Kitsuhon make. This particular bow was wielded by the Faceless Blade, an assassin of the Demon Cult, who carried it to the Marches all the way from her abandoned homeland. It is the weapon of an assassin shooting from the shadows, and is far more precise than most weapons of its ilk. Its arrows are enchanted with a dark vitriol that disrupts spellcasting, making it uniquely suitable for slaying mages.\n\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical Hits with this weapon inflict Silence for 2 turns.",
      "translation": "这把由 Kitsuhon 制造的短弓轻便且易于使用。这把特殊的弓曾由恶魔教派的刺客“无面之刃”使用，她从自己被遗弃的故乡一路带着它来到了边境地区。这种武器非常适合在暗处潜行进行刺杀，其精准度远超同类武器。箭矢上还被施加了某种黑暗的诅咒，这种诅咒会干扰施法者的法术发挥，因此这种弓特别适合用来击杀法师。\n\n        <b>特效</b>使用这种武器造成的暴击会使敌人陷入沉默状态，持续2个回合。",
      "start": 590310,
      "end": 590851,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        A light and wieldy shortbow of Kitsuhon make. This particular bow was wielded by the Faceless Blade, an assassin of the Demon Cult, who carried it to the Marches all the way from her abandoned homeland. It is the weapon of an assassin shooting from the shadows, and is far more precise than most weapons of its ilk. Its arrows are enchanted with a dark vitriol that disrupts spellcasting, making it uniquely suitable for slaying mages.\\n\\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Critical Hits with this weapon inflict Silence for 2 turns.\"",
      "contextKey": "unknown",
      "contextKind": "textify_array",
      "curatedReason": "505_visible_unknown_dialogue",
