      "file": "505.0be08e4a11933fd00e3d.js",
      "category": "dialogue",
      "shouldTranslate": true,
      "original": "A polearm with a wavy bronze blade, set with a pair of malachite stones in its tang and decorated with flowing ribbons. These graceful weapons are a common sight among Jassiran paladins, who first faced the glaive in the fallen land of Arkacia and went on to adopt it as a weapon perfect for a servant of the Lord of Dance.",
      "translation": "这种长柄武器拥有波浪状的青铜刀刃，刀柄上镶嵌着一对孔雀石，同时还装饰着飘逸的丝带。这种优雅的武器在贾西兰的圣骑士们中十分常见——他们最初是在阿卡西亚这片沦陷的土地上首次接触到这种武器，后来便将其视为最适合“舞蹈之主”仆从使用的武器而广泛采用起来。",
      "start": 591322,
      "end": 591647,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"A polearm with a wavy bronze blade, set with a pair of malachite stones in its tang and decorated with flowing ribbons. These graceful weapons are a common sight among Jassiran paladins, who first faced the glaive in the fallen land of Arkacia and went on to adopt it as a weapon perfect for a servant of the Lord of Dance.\"",
