      "original": "\n        A sword-like embodiment of Rimescore which emerges from a crystalline cluster at the edge of a metallic hilt. Cloth twines about the cold-iron handle, providing its wielder with a solid grip and a small reprieve from the frozen metal. Exuding out from the crystalline blade, frozen air spews out like breath from a living creature, billowing forth steadily and rhythmically. When you look at it, you can't shake the feeling that [pc.itemIsEquipped PolarEdge\n            |you're also looking at yourself\n            |it's looking back at you\n        ]. One thing's for certain, though: the glacial might of this crystalline sword is undeniable.\n        \n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Allows the use of <i>Cone of Cold</i>.",
      "translation": "这把剑，正是Rimescore的化身——它的剑身源自金属剑柄边缘的结晶簇中。柔软的布条缠绕在冰冷的铁柄上，既为使用者提供了稳固的握感，也让他们能够稍微远离那冰冷坚硬的金属触感。从那结晶状的剑刃中，仿佛有冷空气不断喷涌而出，就像生物在呼吸一样，稳定而有节奏地流淌着。每当你注视着它的时候，都会不由得产生这样一种感觉…… [pc.itemIsEquipped PolarEdge\n            |你也在审视自己。\n            |它在注视着你。\n        ]不过，有一点是肯定的：这种水晶剑所蕴含的强大力量是不可否认的。\n        \n        <b>特效</b>：允许使用 <i>寒冰锥</i>.",
      "start": 593005,
      "end": 593744,
      "line": 1,
      "raw": "\"\\n        A sword-like embodiment of Rimescore which emerges from a crystalline cluster at the edge of a metallic hilt. Cloth twines about the cold-iron handle, providing its wielder with a solid grip and a small reprieve from the frozen metal. Exuding out from the crystalline blade, frozen air spews out like breath from a living creature, billowing forth steadily and rhythmically. When you look at it, you can't shake the feeling that [pc.itemIsEquipped PolarEdge\\n            |you're also looking at yourself\\n            |it's looking back at you\\n        ]. One thing's for certain, though: the glacial might of this crystalline sword is undeniable.\\n        \\n        <b>Special Effect</b>: Allows the use of <i>Cone of Cold</i>.\"",
